Halo

Scenario: Master Chief has crash landed on the ringworld

Objective 1: Locate and defend Alpha Base

  • Objective 1A: Support scattered UNSC forces
    • Reward 1A: More ally spawns in O2
  • Objective 1B: Sabotage Covenant outposts
    • Reward 1B: Less enemy spawns in O2
  • Objective 1C: Secure underground lightways
    • Reward 1C: More ally reinforcements, less enemy reinforcements in O2

Twist: Captain Keyes is still not at Alpha Base

Objective 2: Locate Captain Keyes

  • Objective 2A: Rescue pinned down UNSC personnel
    • Reward 2A: More ally spawns in Reconciliation
  • Objective 2B: Capture Covenant outposts
    • Reward 2B: Less enemy spawns in Reconciliation
  • Objective 2C: Kill a Sangheili Zealot
    • Reward 2C: O2C automatically completed in Halo

Conclusion: Found a group of Marines that witnessed the Captain get captured
